<P>THE ALGERINE SPY IN PENNSYLVANIA: OR, LETTERS WRITTEN BY A NATIVE OF <HI>ALGIERS</HI> ON THE AFFAIRS OF THE United States in America, FROM THE CLOSE OF THE YEAR 1783 TO THE MEETING OF THE CONVENTION.</P>
