</DIV1>
<DIV1 TYPE="certification">
<PB REF="020481_0003_0FAF1325B2C7D8F0">
<P>I DO certify, that on this twenty-eighth day of Augu&s;t, one thou&s;and &s;even hundred and eighty-&s;even, a book intitled
<Q>The Algerine Spy in Penn&s;ylvania: or, Letters written by a native of Algiers on the affairs of the United States in America, from the clo&s;e of the year 1783 to the meeting of the Conventi|on,</Q>
printed by Prichard and Hall, at Philadelphia, was enter|ed by them in the office of the prothonotary of Philadelphia county as the property of William Prichard.</P>
